1. Clone the Repository

         # To clone

           git clone https://github.com/i-am-monika/automation-with-maven.git
           cd automation-with-maven

2. Build the Project

         # Run the following command to clean and compile the project:

            mvn clean compile

3. Run Unit Tests

         # To execute all unit tests defined in the project:

            mvn test

4. Package the Application

         # To create a .jar file of the application:

            mvn package

5. Run the Application

         # Execute the packaged .jar file:
         
          java -jar target/automation-with-maven-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar
